Trinity::

She smiled, "Your welcome. I got one more left if you want it?" She 
opened her other side comparment.  She got her last little energon 
cube out and tossed it at Nightlight. "Here ya go."

She heard her stomach growl a little. She tried to swat a paw at 
Aerotaur's hand, "Hey, Can I go hunting now?"
